Ｋ 一定要簽 <a href=\"https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbyebuydayhk.github.io%2Fbyebuydayweb%2Fpledge.html&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=16f51100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買可以好有效</span></strong><br />\n如果香港有200萬人=2/7.5人口每星期少2日購物 = 2/7.5*2/7 = 少10%營業額，對鋪租貴既香港地，10%營業額分分鍾就等於商家既50%淨利。另外, 個人消費佔左香港GDP既68%, 如果少10%既消費就等於少左10%既GDP。<br />\n下一季度GPD再負增長,香港將進入Technical Recession。政府冇得唔理。<br />\n<br />\n更加有學者研究指出，罷買只需要全港252,000人集中一日不消費，經濟就會受到好大影響。 (BBC： The '3.5% rule:' How a small minority can change the world.)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買內容（好簡單）</span></strong><br />\n1. 逄星期五、日不花費於日常必須以外的消費<br />\n2. 逄星期五、日不在外食 (上班人士午餐除非可以帶返否則難以避免，但晚餐回家進餐都十分有幫助)<br />\n3. 同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4. 呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n關於我地既報導：<br />\n眾新聞：I Banker（虛構）與網民發起逢周五、日罷買：零成本，希望和理非響應<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zpstHS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zpstHS&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=3a8fe826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zpstHS</a><br />\nＳＣＭＰ既報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U7zPJC&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=a7ae9e40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/1ta7DfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ta7DfO.jpg&h=470d5d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/5OkGHHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi